name: Cyclops Canyon
description:
Introduction

Very spectacular & exciting canyon to do as a First Desent - the canyon precipitously descends over an immense vertical drop. The wall here is over 700 feet high. We did this section with three rappels (one after another) - using a 250', 50' & a 350' rappel sequence & a down-climb
